\subsection{Costs}

\subsubsection{A spy must spend (250 + 150 \x Rank) Silver Pennies per
year to maintain a proper set of thieving equipment.}

A spy who does not spend the above amount operates as if he
were two Ranks less proficient when performing any of the abilities
described in \ref{spy:picklocks}, \ref{spy:removetraps} and
\ref{spy:pickpockets}. If his Rank for these abilities is
temporarily reduced to a negative number, he may not perform them
until he meets expenses.

The above cost does not include any trap containers (see the Basic
Goods Cost List) that the spy may wish to purchase.
